    "4010025": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Dehya and Candace",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Oh, it just occurred to me that we should also get you a makeup box."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Candace",
                    "T": "No, it's fine. I don't think I'll end up using it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Maybe you won't, but it doesn't hurt to have one, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "C'mon, just trust me on this one..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Huh? Who are you, and what do you want?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Layla",
                    "T": "Pâ€”Please... don't move..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "\"Don't move\"? Who sent you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Candace",
                    "T": "Dehya..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Don't worry, I can handle this. Now, tell me, what do you want?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Candace",
                    "T": "I believe she's looking for this. Here, take it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Aâ€”A butterfly? Was it on my head?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Layla",
                    "T": "Oh, you'reâ€”"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Candace",
                    "T": "It's been a while, Layla."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "A friend of yours? Oh, so she must be the one you were telling me about..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? You two know each other?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Layla",
                    "T": "Oh, yeah... it has been some time. The first time I ever woke up after sleepwalking, I somehow found myself in Aaru Village. Candace was the one who took care of me then."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Candace",
                    "T": "That's right. She didn't look well, so I gave her something to eat. She said a lot of complicated things about astrology, the night sky, the stars... Not sure I understood it all, but it sounded pretty enchanting."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Candace",
                    "T": "Right, do you still want this butterfly? It seems like you were chasing it all the way here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Candace",
                    "T": "It's of little use to me, but if you don't want it, I can release it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Just let her have it. It's no big deal."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The Swiftfly was flying so fast, but you were able to catch it like it was nothing, Candace."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Candace",
                    "T": "It didn't seem that quick, really. I was actually worried that I would injure it, but I'm glad that didn't happen."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "Anyway, sorry about the butterfly thing. With the way you suddenly came running over like that, I thought you were hired to take us out or something."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "On second thought, I guess I've never seen an assassin that looks tired with dark bags around their eyes... Oh, you must be taking part in the Championship? Take it from me, don't let it stop you from getting some rest."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Layla",
                    "T": "I'll do what I can. Thank you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Dehya",
                    "T": "We'll be on our way, then. See you later."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alrighty. Let's bring the Swiftfly back together with Layla!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
